Baraza Project

Objective: Create a business unit applet and servlet application based on XML

The project is divided into four large parts which are subdivided

1. Applet application
a. application, login and main menu
b. input forms - form, grid, filter
c. reports
d. process management

2. Servlet Application
a. The application which has the login and the main menu structure
b. the report and hyperlink tables or action event tables
c. the input forms

3. Server
a. Mail server
b. Process server
c. webserver

4. IDE
a. XML Integrated Development Enviroment


